Microservices using Spring Boot

Intro  https://spring.io/microservices


Microservices concepts: (Spring Boot v3) 
1. Communication - Eureka server & client
2. Configuration - Spring Cloud Config server
3. Fault tolerance - Resilience4j
4. Routing	- Zuul
5. Event driven - Spring Cloud Stream, Kafka
6. Observability - Micrometer, Zipkin
7. Security - OAuth2, JWT
8. Deployment - Cloud Foundry, Docker, Kubernates
9. Monitoring - Prometheus, Grafana
10.Logging - ELK


